{"tid":722669,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"波神畀料：2018神作 - 絕命酒店","createTime":"2018-06-29T16:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T16:45:45.000Z","uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9346302db65a1d78bf56c0c85a62db4b4a7a60b3","tid":722669,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"相信大家有睇過動漫，對魔法戰爭都唔陌生，呢套絕命酒店，就好比動漫界既魔法戰爭，2個字，神作！<br />\n<br />\n絕命酒店，一開始就講Rule係好重要，但規矩個重要性，應該排在道德之上，定之下呢？<br />\n你係醫生，發現個病人係你仇人，你救定殺？<br />\n你係刺客，準備刺殺目標時，佢開十倍價錢，要求放過自己，你應該點選？<br />\n情人誤殺自己細佬，你會否原諒佢？<br />\n<br />\n我希望仲未睇過 絕命酒店既巴打，快d去睇一次，你第一次未必睇得明哂，唔重要，再入場睇多次，再唔明，再入去睇。<br />\n睇到落畫都唔明點算？<br />\n睇 魔法戰爭！<br />\n我相信，到時你地一定會明，仲會有好多說話想講，到時搵返呢個post，講下你既得著。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/005711_054a968fbc98a0c7e72262bd59f8cf92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F005711_054a968fbc98a0c7e72262bd59f8cf92.png&h=f2b28d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用開呢個app，就知呢個app係香港清泉，絕冇打手，見到有4.1分，唔睇就笨！"},{"pid":"6904603eeda7f4a343e6e73c0d743f8a12069f0e","tid":722669,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T23:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce69d97f3e2ec17b175f0203d5bfc53b7d2f4bb","tid":722669,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"伏撚到喊<br />\n戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"763535b66df72549d27514fed6f7b405a3cebc3a","tid":722669,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ce69d97f3e2ec17b175f0203d5bfc53b7d2f4bb","tid":722669,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"伏撚到喊<br />\n戇鳩鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"自睇唔明就話伏"},{"pid":"39c8b14bf34a5e26ce5ceda149a55580fa66a5a2","tid":722669,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ce69d97f3e2ec17b175f0203d5bfc53b7d